snippet.textDisplay: If you still want a darker root get a DEMI-permanent color 2 shades darker than the level you have now so maybe about, a level 6 Demi permanent color (since your about an 8 now from what I can see) & tap it on your roots (with an actual hair color brush, no hands cause you can stain the rest of the blonde & u can buy a hair color brush from Sally’s as well) ANYWAY after you tap it on your roots, take a WIDE TOOTH COMB or a hair pick (not a hairbrush or fine tooth comb) & brush it through the hair starting at the root to blend it into the rest of your hair so that you don’t have a line of demarcation ♥️ hope this helps!!              Ps. When you purchase the Demi permanent in a level 6 it usually looks like ‘6N’ meaning level 6 natural or like ‘6NG’ meaning level 6 natural gold or something like that it depends on the color line but usually it’s something along those lines ✨
